column2: SELECT TOP # Artist.Name as artist, SUM(Track.UnitPrice) as price, Album.AlbumId as album FROM chinook.Track INNER JOIN chinook.Album on chinook.Album.AlbumId=chinook.Track.AlbumId INNER JOIN chinook.Artist on chinook.Artist.ArtistId=chinook.Album.ArtistId GROUP BY Track.UnitPrice, Artist.Name, Album.AlbumId ORDER BY SUM(Track.UnitPrice) DESC
